\n<br />\n日本普遍低賤工作來講時薪900-1300啦 睇地方"},{"pid":"83b89a8d022cb78f57107d1540bdb94e2027a4fd","tid":422244,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:12:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登真係好撚低質呀屌<br />\n佢賺到幾錢根本唔係重點<br />\n重點係佢終於肯踏出第一步<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n後生已經有咁既思想其實幾悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14e67e700e01994a6fc3f3c007e6b0b5963d3df","tid":422244,"uid":50208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:13:04.000Z","msg":"佢老豆死左五年先出去搵野做 咁仲關唔關佢老豆死事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbafabb7ccc86510594f3b40c2754f97b4bf98d6","tid":422244,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:13:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"267af622c297f4d165c1fd36917631c49c60233a","tid":422244,"uid":111768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:15:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5000😂佢五做好過做拉😅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港就係有你呢啲口臭閪先咁折墮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔撚識講野就收下把口啦低智撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇你都係現實被人杯葛果類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21faaab6346c42b85381285bd8b227104a39d5c","tid":422244,"uid":53736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:15:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本倭寇眞係多垃圾</blockquote><br />\n望下上面鬼國仲撚多啦臭雞五毛"},{"pid":"551e3c1bc0a74b77b2913e0a11c8bec2a5a6b64a","tid":422244,"uid":72519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:19:33.000Z","msg":"咁似我<br />\n好怕第時都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21081aad07ba5923ac28183d7da8a789447c011c","tid":422244,"uid":120202,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:24:16.000Z","msg":"好想攬住佢比好多愛同勇氣佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油啊"},{"pid":"58cb26c304b0e009fec90c5064987184f8578bd3","tid":422244,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:28:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><strong>45歲領到第一份薪水！　日女捧5000元淚崩：我是有用的</strong><br />\n<br />\n日本京都一名45歲女子，宅在家中超過20年，今（2017）年5月終於離家工作，領到第一份薪水，手裡捧著5000日圓（新台幣1350元），淚崩喊「原來我還是有用的」。據了解，她從高中時代就無法融入群體生活，不敢與人相處，導致長期惡性循環，直到5年前父親癌症逝世，才努力求職，最終找到每周3天發傳單的工作。<br />\n<br />\n根據《朝日新聞》報導，這名「宅女」高中時無法融入班上，壓力大到常常肚子痛，連上廁所都被同學嘲笑「好臭」，這個挫敗的人際關係，導致她越來越不敢與人相處，更別說去認識新朋友，一直到大學都無法改善，沒想到畢業後應徵30間公司也都沒有錄取，讓她越來越害怕「外面的世界」。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，她自從求職碰壁後，就將自己關在家裡，平常幫家人做家事，沒事則待在房間上網，直到5年前父親罹癌過世，才發現這種日子也是有結束的一天，透過團體協助，終於在5月找到工作，每周3天發傳單，旁人不斷鼓勵她「你很努力」、「幸好有妳幫忙」，終於走出陰影。<br />\n<br />\n這名女子6月初收到第一份薪水，手中捧著5000日圓，身體不斷發抖，再也忍不住的哭出來，說她也是被人需要的。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n3x4=12,返12日工，得 5000yen?</blockquote><br />\n派傳單應該part time呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354deb2665a3a8783e23ad7e5f84686b47c9e32b","tid":422244,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"無相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8890a4e520e89fb7cad5f83c9e32d4e672dbe982","tid":422244,"uid":83440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢老豆死左五年先出去搵野做 咁仲關唔關佢老豆死事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會係因為用曬啲錢"},{"pid":"dcfdc8030490937b59280ffe736763e95069504e","tid":422244,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:31:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常，因為要保護當事人身分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/no.gi